public enum BookStatus
extends java.lang.Enum<BookStatus>

Enumerates the possible returned statuses of an attempted booking operation.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Lars Kuettner
See Also:
BusinessServices.book(long, suncertify.services.Contractor)

Enum Constant Summary
INTERMITTENTLY_DELETED
          Contractor record intermittently deleted indicating the decision to book this record being based on stale information.
INTERMITTENTLY_GRABBED
          Contractor record intermittently grabbed (booked) by another agent and thus not booked by the current caller.
INTERMITTENTLY_UPDATED
          Contractor record intermittently updated or even replaced as record numbers are recycled.
SUCCESSFULLY_BOOKED
          Contractor record successfully booked.
